OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to get medical
OL,4,Ccannabis in the UK?
OL,6,FIn 2018, medical cannabis was
OL,7,Flegalised in the UK.JAnd yet, six
OL,8,Fyears on, families are going bankrupt
OL,9,Fas they struggle to get hold of the
OL,10,Fdrug and pay for their prescriptions.
OL,11,FThat's because current NHS regulation
OL,12,Fmeans barely anyone can access free
OL,13,Ftreatment, forcing many to turn to
OL,14,Fprivate prescriptions.JSo, why is it
OL,15,Fso restrictive? And how can things be
OL,16,Fchanged?
